description: This file initializes a React application by rendering the main App component into the DOM element with id 'root'. It sets up the rendering root using ReactDOM.createRoot and wraps the App component within React's StrictMode for highlighting potential problems.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a React root for the application rendering.

methods.name: React.StrictMode
methods.description: Wraps components to activate additional checks and warnings for child components.
